This was adapted from a mirror of: http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=90 and modernized with JJ support.

Neovim plugin useful for manipulating files controlled by JJ (Jujutsu), SVN, git, and hg within Neovim, including committing changes and performing diffs using the vimdiff system.

Keywords: jj jujutsu git mercurial hg subversion SVN vcscommand VCS

The source for the original version of this plugin was available in git at git://repo.or.cz/vcscommand .  A web front end was available at http://repo.or.cz/w/vcscommand.git .

